Subject: [liste-egc] 2 long-term Post-Doc positions in NLP at the Center for
 Human Language Technology and Bio-informatics =?UTF-8?Q?=28Covilh=C3=A3?=
 =?UTF-8?Q?=2C?= Portugal).

(*Apologies for cross-postings*)

The Center for Human Language Technology and Bio-informatics of the
University of Beira Interior (Covilh達, Portugal) is currently opening
calls for 2 long-term Post-Doc positions in the field of Natural
Language Processing.

-------------------
Available Positions
-------------------

* [Post-Doc #1] * 3-year Post-Doc position in Machine Learning, Natural
Language Processing and Social Networks

The successful candidate will integrate to the POCI-01-0145-FEDER-028918
project that aims to study and develop a multilingual surveillance
system capable of detecting emerging crowds by identifying rising events
that foster high focus, high energy and high emotion on social media.

* [Post-Doc #2] * 2-year Post-Doc position in Natural Language
Processing and Cloud Computing

The successful candidate will integrate the C4 - Cloud Computing
Competences Center, co-funded by the Portugal 2020 Program (PT 2020) and
will develop scientific and technological research tasks related a Cloud
Computing Platform for Linguistic Services.

------------
Requirements
------------

Candidates must have a Ph.D. degree in Computer Science, Data Science,
Applied Mathematics or any related field not older than 4 years at the
time of application.

In case that the Ph.D. defense is not yet finished, the candidate must
also provide an official letter certifying that his/her Ph.D. thesis has
already been submitted for defense and outlining the expected schedule
of the Ph.D. defense.

All candidates are expected to be fluent in English, while prior
knowledge of Portuguese is not required. Candidates will be evaluated on
the ground of their strong international research record, and preference
will be given to those whose research areas match the research
directions of both positions.

------------------
Context and Salary
------------------

Covilh達 is an attractive city surrounded by splendid mountains with ski
facilities (http://www.cm-covilha.pt/). It is also very attractive for
students and young researchers as it provides an exceptional natural
environment.

The average net salary in Portugal is around 900 euros/month and both
positions propose high level salaries for Portuguese standards.

* [Post-Doc #1] * Net salary = 2100 euros/month
* [Post-Doc #2] * Net salary = 1500 euros/month

-----------
Application
-----------

Applications must be submitted electronically to the coordinator of the
project: Dr. Sebasti達o Pais (sebastiao@di.ubi.pt). The applicants should
provide the following documents with their application:

- An academic CV, a list of publications, and a motivation letter.
- A scanned copy of the Ph.D. diploma, or a letter certifying
submission of doctoral thesis for the defense, and
- Two reference letters.

---------------
Important Dates
---------------

Deadline for application: February 15, 2019.

----------------------
Additional Information
----------------------

For any further information, please contact directly the coordinator of
the project: Dr. Sebasti達o Pais (sebastiao@di.ubi.pt).


